703610f-b.title: Brooklyn: Classon Avenue - Myrtle Avenue
703610f-b.text:
Classon Ave., south from No. 212 at right foreground, just south oof Myrtle Ave. The building at right is a part of the Fleischmann's Yeast Corporation. St. Mary'e Episcopal Church is seen in the
background at the N.W. corner of,Willoughby Ave.
1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
